captureOn()	; FU-9 (D-6): 1 iff the RING should capture now — armed AND not auto-disabled.
"RTN","VSLTAP",145,0)
	; doc: @returns bool  the ALWAYS-ON capture gate. The ring records whenever the tap
"RTN","VSLTAP",146,0)
